
## 6) `.gitignore`

```text
# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs
*.log

# Temp files
*.tmp
*.swp
*.bak

# Environment files
.env
.env.*

# Sensitive files
config.php
secrets.txt
credentials.txt
*.pem
*.key
id_rsa
id_rsa.pub

# Tailscale sensitive exports
tailscale-authkey.txt
tailscale-state.json

# Archives
*.zip
*.tar
*.gz
*.7z

# Editor folders
.vscode/
.idea/
